Bitcoin.Travel is a Google Maps-based interactive bitcoin directory service of physical locations which accept and deal with Bitcoins.

Service provides a members area, which is a private area where our global membership can gain access to the latest member services. It enables to add and edit listings of bitcoin businesses in seconds. Users can register on site and easily manage the places they have listed, so that the information provided is up-to-date.

Bitcoin directory of hotels, restaurants, nightclubs, stores and other businesses in tourism industry, accepting Bitcoins around the world.

Travel for bitcoins!

##History

This service was first offered on July, 2011

